Shortcuts for quick launch Technology keyboard launcher.

Add keyboard shortcut commands to quickly Launch Howtogeek (Alt + G), Launch Imore (Alt + I), Launch macrumors.com (Alt + R)

This extension will help you access it faster and easier.
